## Store Credit [/v1/customer/{id}/payment-methods/store-credits]

+ Parameters
    + id: 1 (required, number) - Customer ID

### List [GET /v1/customer/{id}/payment-methods/store-credits{?size,from,sortBy}]

+ Parameters
    + size:   1           (optional, number)       - Page size.
    + from:   1           (optional, number)       - Start element (counting from 0) or # of elements to skip.
    + sortBy: `createdAt` (optional, enum[string]) - Field to sort by (`-fieldName` for descending order).
        + Members
            + `id`
            + `originId`
            + `originType`
            + `customerId`
            + `currency`
            + `originalBalance`
            + `currentBalance`
            + `availableBalance`
            + `canceledAmount`
            + `canceledReason`
            + `state`
            + `createdAt`
+ Response 200 (application/json)
  + Attributes (StoreCreditsWithTotals)

### View [GET /v1/store-credits/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 1 (required, number) - Store Credit ID
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (StoreCredit)

### Update State [PATCH /v1/store-credits/{id}]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (StoreCreditUpdateStatePayload)
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (StoreCredit)

### Bulk Update State [PATCH /v1/store-credits]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (StoreCreditBulkStateUpdatePayload)
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[StoreCreditBulkResponse])

### List Transactions [GET /v1/store-credits/{id}/transactions/{?size,from,sortBy}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 1 (required, number)                     - Store Credit ID.
    + size:   1           (optional, number)       - Page size.
    + from:   1           (optional, number)       - Start element (counting from 0) or # of elements to skip.
    + sortBy: `createdAt` (optional, enum[string]) - Field to sort by (`-fieldName` for descending order).
        + Members
            + `id`
            + `storeCreditId`
            + `orderPaymentId`
            + `debit`
            + `availableBalance`
            + `state`
            + `createdAt`
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (StoreCreditAdjustments)
